title: Libre Computer Unveils Amlogic-Powered AML-A311D-CC Alta SBC
description: Libre Computer’s AML-A311D-CC Alta, part of the Cottonwood series, is a low-cost single board computer equipped with integrated CPU, GPU, and 5 TOPs NPU cores. It is designed to deliver high-performance computing suitable for applications requiring 4K video processing and AI workload capabilities.
